Michael Sitrick CoIf there is anything you need or any way I can help please do not hesitate to call There are few leaders who have succeeded through business transformationsin particular trasformations that require internal cultures of disruptiveness or reinvention You are one of the few You have always demonstrated the ability and the willingness to take bold moves in redefining Enron and redefining the energy business I believe Sitrick can be extremely helpful to you and the company I have used them and have seen their ability to redefine events and organize a PR defense and offense in difficult situations I told Mike Sitrick to expect a call from you and asked him to personally as the owner and CEO of the company to handle Enron You have my support
EnronYou still have my support Let me know if I can be helpful in any way
